125
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,120
I think it means,

126
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,710
if you repay the loan,

127
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:25,710
China wins.

128
00:05:25,710 --> 00:05:27,380
If you can’t repay,

129
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:29,150
China also wins.

130
00:05:29,150 --> 00:05:30,150
Win-win.

